{
  "texts": [
    "10 We follow Bozarth and Budak (2022)'s procedure to identify SMO accounts.",
    "Specifically, the Crowd Counting Consortium data for most protest events includes the name of the SMO that organized the event.",
    "We then use the Twitter Search API to retrieve likely Twitter account matches for organizers of all protest events between 2017-2019 in any of the three issue areas.",
    "Out of 1.48M tweets classified as relevant, 4,218 are labeled with the journalist author role and 5,817 with the SMO author role.",
    "The remaining tweets are labeled with the other author role."
  ]
}